[Episode 38]

3
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:39,800
There's one month left

4
00:01:40,229 --> 00:01:41,360
to the half-year bet

5
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:43,830
you made with Mr. Gu.

6
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:45,120
I said you will head over

7
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,050
after the seventh day of mourning.

8
