and smoked food,

74
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:26,360
requiring large amounts of salt.

75
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,700
Since we're opening a salt shop,

76
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,480
why not

77
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,330
open in these places?

78
00:04:32,820 --> 00:04:33,820
That makes sense.

79
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,830
The salt licenses from Lianghuai

80
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,790
also bear the Qing seal.

81
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:38,830
Moreover,

82
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,600
the ban on provincial monopolies

83
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,730
has been abolished.

84
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:44,159
As the saying goes,
businessmen should travel the world.

85
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,480
Staying in one province

86
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,940
is being too restrictive.

87
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:48,600
I understand now.

88
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,840
Are you taking us

89
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,360
to do transprovincial business?

90
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,970
If Li Wantang can cross the Yangtze River

91
00:04:52,970 --> 00:04:54,800
to acquire our Lianghuai salt fields,

92
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,630
what's so special

93
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:56,830
about what I'm doing?

94
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,690
If we had thought of this earlier,

95
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,410
why would we have been at odds

96
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,540
with Li for so long?

97
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:03,190
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

98
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,400
This solution

99
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,470
has been there all along.

100
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:08,600
If he hadn't pushed me

101
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,510
to the edge,

102
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:12,890
I wouldn't want to deal with him this way.

103
00:05:14,690 --> 00:05:16,040
I don't even want

104
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,070
to be the Viceroy of Liangjiang anymore.

105
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,930
Let's go make a fortune together.

106
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,110
Sir.

107
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,270
If you're done looking at it,

108
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,470
please let me go home.

109
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,360
My family is still in mourning.

110
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,650
How could you be like this?

111
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,690
It's fine, it's fine.

112
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:29,830
If not now,

113
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:30,960
I'll go back with you

114
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:33,040
to pay respects to Old Madam Gu.

115
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,920
What could she possibly say about me?

116
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:37,520
You're just taking advantage
of my abilities.

117
00:05:40,430 --> 00:05:41,690
Is Gu in there?

118
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,560
All the filial sons in the world

119
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,720
are reporting here.

120
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,050
Young Master Li,

121
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:01,630
weren't you going to come
only after the seventh day of mourning?

122
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:02,120
Sir,

123
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,530
I'm here to check the accounts.

124
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:08,800
Sure.

125
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,590
Go ahead.

126
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:13,980
Take your time.

127
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,370
You stay right here.

128
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,310
Guards!

129
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,480
-Yes!
-Yes!

130
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:29,830
Guard the door carefully.

131
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,290
Sharpen your blades well.

132
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,690
No one can leave today.

133
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,690
They can leave,

134
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,830
but not alive.

135
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:37,030
Yes, sir!

136
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:49,159
Your idea

137
00:06:49,630 --> 00:06:50,600
is excellent.

138
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:51,870
Some days ago,

139
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:54,240
I also submitted
a memorial to the imperial court

140
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,970
requesting to build railways.

141
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:58,120
Once goods can circulate freely,

142
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,560
and merchants can trade everywhere,

143
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,290
our people will become wealthy

144
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:03,520
and commoners will live better lives.

145
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:08,550
The imperial court is planning to establish
a Ministry of Commerce.

146
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,710
I think

147
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,800
the Minister of Commerce...

148
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,120
Sir, if you continue this talk,

149
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,160
I'll bash my head
against the wall right now.

150
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,430
Being such a minor official

151
00:07:16,430 --> 00:07:17,140
has already exhausted me

152
00:07:17,140 --> 00:07:18,360
to the point of vomiting and diarrhea.

153
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:20,430
And now you want me
to go serve as an official in the capital?

154
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:22,030
You might as well kill me now.

155
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,260
Didn't we agree

156
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,560
that once I help you
accomplish this matter,

157
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,360
you would let me return to Anhui?

158
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:29,990
How can you...

159
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:31,950
How can you have no ambition

160
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:32,870
at all?

161
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,870
This regime

162
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,330
is not one for business.

163
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:40,760
We're different from foreigners.

164
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:48,210
That's insightful.

165
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:50,070
To be honest with you,

166
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:52,950
I've been telling the imperial court
the same thing.

167
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,510
I said we can't keep clinging to

168
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:56,190
Mencius's old doctrines anymore.

169
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,550
Always going on about

170
00:07:57,570 --> 00:07:58,920
righteousness versus profit,

171
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,720
and gentlemen versus petty men.

172
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,720
People are doing business with us

173
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,480
holding guns

174
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:04,580
and cannons.

175
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:06,120
Yet here we are, still talking to them

176
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,070
about Confucius and Mencius foolishly.

177
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:08,730
Do you think this makes sense?

178
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,000
The Minister of Commerce

179
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:14,350
is a high-ranking official.

180
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,480
If you're lucky,

181
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,680
in just a few years,

182
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,980
you'll be my equal.

183
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,600
What's good about

184
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:24,360
being in a position like yours?

185
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,390
Aren't you just worried every day

186
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:27,720
about your own fortune?

187
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,380
I don't have that confidence.

188
00:08:30,670 --> 00:08:31,240
Sir.

189
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:33,130
I'm just a man with no ambition.

190
00:08:33,130 --> 00:08:33,669
No,

191
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,789
you're not.

192
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,490
Alright, that's for later.

193
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,909
We don't need to discuss it now.

194
00:08:38,909 --> 00:08:39,549
However,

195
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,809
in reorganizing the Salt Industry Guild,

196
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:45,220
your contribution has been tremendous.

197
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,000
I plan

198
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:47,750
to give you 20%

199
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,510
of the Salt Industry Guild shares.

200
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,670
Aren't you happy?

201
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,030
Sir.

202
00:08:52,980 --> 00:08:54,780
The outcome is still uncertain.

203
