228
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,960
Regarding the mortgage,

229
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,720
both parties

230
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:09,210
have different opinions.

231
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,650
