244
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,120
Mr. Richard,

245
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,580
after all your years here,

246
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,520
you must surely understand that

247
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:43,790
in the Great Qing,

248
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:45,630
a business without official backing

249
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:46,360
that grows too large

250
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,360
is nothing more than

251
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,360
